<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="A" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Aweary" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Aweary,</orth> weary, tired, fatigued: <cit><quote>I am a., give me leave a while,</quote> <bibl n="shak. rom 2.5.25" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. II, 5, 25</bibl></cit>. Followed by <emph>of,</emph> == tired of: <cit><quote>I am a. of this moon,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mnd 5.255" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. V, 255</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. mv 1.2.2" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. I, 2, 2</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. aww 1.3.47" default="NO" valid="yes">All's I, 3, 47</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. aww 4.5.59" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 5, 59</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 3.2.88" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A III, 2, 88</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 4.2.7" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. IV, 2, 7</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jc 4.3.95" default="NO" valid="yes">Caes. IV, 3, 95</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 5.5.49" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. V, 5, 49</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>